languages.text: "Может, и не верю. Но откуда-то же они появляются? Кто-то что-то видел... или хочет заставить других считать, что видел".
"Maybe I don't. But the rumours are coming from somewhere, so somebody must have seen something... Or just wants others to believe they did."
languages.original_text: "Может, и не верю. Но откуда-то же они появляются? Кто-то что-то видел... или хочет заставить других считать, что видел".

languages.text: “或许我并没有，但传言都不是无凭无据的。所以，肯定是有人看到了什么……或者，他们只是想让别人相信他们看到了什么。”
languages.original_text: "Maybe I don't. But the rumours are coming from somewhere, so somebody must have seen something... Or just wants others to believe they did."

languages.text: «Pues igual no, pero los rumores salen de alguna parte, así que alguien ha visto algo... o quiere que los demás creamos que lo ha visto».
languages.original_text: "Maybe I don't. But the rumours are coming from somewhere, so somebody must have seen something... Or just wants others to believe they did."

languages.text: 「どうだかな。でも噂はどこからか出てくるもんだから、誰かが何かを見たのは確かだろう…もしくは、見たことを信じてもらいたがっているとか」
languages.original_text: "Maybe I don't. But the rumours are coming from somewhere, so somebody must have seen something... Or just wants others to believe they did."

traits.locale_text: 「どうだかな。でも噂はどこからか出てくるもんだから、誰かが何かを見たのは確かだろう…もしくは、見たことを信じてもらいたがっているとか」

languages.text: "Vielleicht nicht. Aber die Gerüchte kommen von irgendwoher, also muss jemand was gesehen haben ... oder will zumindest, dass andere es glauben."
languages.original_text: "Maybe I don't. But the rumours are coming from somewhere, so somebody must have seen something... Or just wants others to believe they did."

traits.locale_text: "Vielleicht nicht. Aber die Gerüchte kommen von irgendwoher, also muss jemand was gesehen haben ... oder will zumindest, dass andere es glauben."

languages.text: « J'ai rien dit de tel, mais y a pas de fumée sans feu, et ces rumeurs viennent pas de nulle part. Un membre de l'équipage a dû voir quelque chose... Ou alors, c'est ce qu'on veut nous faire croire. »
languages.original_text: "Maybe I don't. But the rumours are coming from somewhere, so somebody must have seen something... Or just wants others to believe they did."

languages.text: "Tamam, inanmıyoruz da bu söylentiler bir yerden çıkıyor sonuçta. Belli ki birileri bir şey görmüş... Ya da milleti öyle olduğuna inandırmak istiyor."
languages.original_text: "Maybe I don't. But the rumours are coming from somewhere, so somebody must have seen something... Or just wants others to believe they did."

traits.locale_text: "İnanmıyorum belki ama dedikodular da bir yerlerden çıkıyor sonuçta, birileri bir şeyler görmüş ya da diğerlerini bir şeyler gördüğüne inandırmak istiyor olmalı."
